\section{
  \title{Cadet\aux{ (\code{project.concourse-ci.org})}}

  \link{Cadet}{https://project.concourse-ci.org} is a deployment of
  \link{\code{vito/cadet}}{https://github.com/vito/cadet}, a side-project for
